source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_SEQ_00<tab>Angry Coeurl regards you with suspicion.
TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_TODO_00<tab>Speak with Frightened Coeurl in Grymm & Enid.
TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_TODO_01<tab>Pick up the unconscionably heavy sacks.
TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_TODO_02<tab>Deliver the unconscionably heavy sacks to Angry Coeurl.
TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_001<tab>A new face in Ala Gannha? Huh... What would you ask of me, then?
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_001<tab>Dich habe ich hier noch nie gesehen. Was willst du von mir?

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_002<tab>A stranger and a generous soul besides? Bollocks. There's naught more suspicious than a good samaritan.
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_002<tab>Du willst mir helfen? ...<var 1D /var>Du führst doch was im Schilde, oder? Mach, dass du wegkommst, bevor ich<var 1D /var>...

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_003<tab>...On the other hand, if you were an imperial agent, I expect you'd go about your business with more discretion. Bugger me, you really are here to help, aren't you?
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_003<tab>Nein, warte. Es gibt da etwas. Du willst also wirklich helfen?

source:
TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_004Very well. I'll take you up on your offer, stranger...
My little brother's working the rocks by Grymm & Enid. He's got something for me. Can you go and get it?
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_004<tab>Kennst du den Teich im Südwesten? Wir nennen ihn Grymm und Enid. Mein Bruder Ängstlicher Coeurl hat dort etwas <var 1A 02 /var>gefunden<var 1A 01 /var>.

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_005<tab>Right, then. Frightened Coeurl is his name. Ask him for the leftovers─he ought to understand.
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_005<tab>Ich möchte, dass du es mir bringst. Alles klar? Worauf wartest du dann noch?

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_010<tab>You know where Grymm & Enid are, aye? West by southwest. Look for the bastard what looks like me, but less handsome.
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_010<tab>Du hast doch versprochen, meinen Bruder Ängstlicher Coeurl am Grymm und Enid zu treffen und mir zu bringen, was er <var 1A 02 /var>gefunden<var 1A 01 /var> hat.

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_FRIGHTENEDCOEURL_000_020<tab>Hm? Here for the leftovers, are you? Not like my brother to send someone in his stead, but so be it.
TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_FRIGHTENEDCOEURL_000_021<tab>It's all in the sacks over yonder. They're bleedin' heavy, mind, so be careful when you pick 'em up.
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_FRIGHTENEDCOEURL_000_021<tab>Da, das ist, was ich<var 1D /var>... äh, <var 1A 02 /var>gefunden<var 1A 01 /var> habe. Bring das zu meinem Bruder, ja? Und nicht verlieren!

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_FRIGHTENEDCOEURL_000_030<tab>The sacks you'll be wantin' to take back to Ala Gannha are over there. Hope you brought a pack bird.
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_FRIGHTENEDCOEURL_000_030<tab>Bitte bring <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8DD9020502 /var> zu meinem Bruder Zorniger Coeurl. Lass ihn nicht warten, er kann etwas aufbrausend sein.

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_040<tab>Ah, the new face. You have my leftovers?
TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_041<tab>Huh, well I'll be...you actually went and brought the whole lot. Much obliged, much obliged...
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_041<tab>Uff, ganz schön schwer. Na, vielen Dank.

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_042<tab>It's saltpeter for making firesand, in case you're curious what it's all for. The rocks by the lakes've got good deposits.
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_042<tab>Was da drin ist? Salpeter. Du weißt schon, woraus man Schießpulver macht.

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_043<tab>'Tain't hard for my brother to pass for any other plodding quarryman, all the while sweeping bits and pieces off to the side, to bundle up and sell to the sutlers what trade with the Resistance.
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_043<tab>Im Steinbruch werden immer wieder kleine Mengen davon gewonnen. Sag's nicht weiter, aber einer der Arbeiter dort füllt es uns ab und überlässt es uns. Wir verkaufen den Salpeter dann an einen Händler, der ab und zu mal hier vorbeikommt, und der verkauft ihn an die Be<var 16 /var>freiungs<var 16 /var>armee.

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_044<tab>It's a living, and a way of fighting back besides. Our way of spitting in the Garleans' eye for putting our father in an imperial uniform and shipping him off to some faraway province fifteen years ago.
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_044<tab>Mein Bruder und ich hassen das Kaiserreich<var 1D /var>... haben auch allen Grund dazu. Unser Vater wurde vor fünfzehn Jahren in die garleische Armee zwangsrekrutiert und auf einen blutigen Kriegszug irgendwo in ein fernes Land geschickt.

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_045<tab>Dunno if he's dead or alive, even. Though, if he were alive, he'd not be long for this world if we were caught fighting for the Resistance. So this is the best we can do.
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_045<tab>Also helfen wir der Be<var 16 /var>freiungs<var 16 /var>armee, wo wir können. Nur mitkriegen soll es keiner. Wir haben Angst, dass man unseren Vater bestrafen würde.

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_046<tab>...That's the long and the short of it. We do what we can, though we know it's not enough.
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_046<tab>Dabei wissen wir nicht einmal, ob er noch lebt<var 1D /var>...

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_047<tab>I think you'll find that most folks here ain't much different. Everybody's got a reason, but in the end, the result is the same.
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_047<tab>Hier im Dorf sind viele, die die Garlear hassen. Jeder hat einen Grund dazu. Aber das heißt nicht, dass jeder bereit ist, gegen sie zu kämpfen. Es steht zu viel auf dem Spiel.

source: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_048<tab>I suppose I just...I just wanted you to know, is all. That I─that we know why you're here, and that even if we can't join you, we...we wish we could...
target: TEXT_STMBDA128_02955_ANGRYCOEURL_000_048<tab>Jedenfalls vielen Dank für deine Hilfe. Hoffen wir, dass die Jungs in Rhalgrs Wacht etwas mit dem Schießpulver anzufangen wissen.
